		<h2>About Reporting Requirements</h2>
		
		<p>The TVFC Program requires TVFC providers to monitor the temperatures of all refrigerators and freezers containing TVFC vaccines and to submit reports to their responsible entity (DSHS HSR or LHD) utilizing TVFC Program forms documenting vaccine inventory and usage.</p>
		
