			<li>Temperature Recording Form (EC-105), including
				<ul>
					<li>Refrigerator Fahrenheit (EC-105RF)</li>
					<li>Refrigerator Celsius (EC-105RC)</li>
					<li>Freezer Fahrenheit (EC-105FF)</li>
					<li>Freezer Celsius (EC-105FC)</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>Any other reports or required documents</li>
		</ul>
		<p>All forms are available on the <a title="TVFC Forms and Publications" href="/immunize/tvfc/publications.aspx">TVFC Forms and Publications</a> page.</p>
		
